    "0x7274d0": "attract_scene_lifecycle = attract top scene の lifecycle(init/update/shutdown, +4=state)。demo browser(0x725fa0)を回し離脱条件(attract_exit_input_trigger/+0xb8)で exit flag(+0x15)。vtable-dispatch ゆえ直接呼出元なし。※title「画面をタッチしてください」は別 scene(scene_diag で attract=0)",
    "0x725fa0": "attract_demo_browser = attract demo ページ巡回(FUN_00725d60=advertise_demo_controller を case3 で駆動)。touch は demo 循環に消費",
    "0x728700": "attract_exit_input_trigger = attract 離脱トリガ。DAT_016f5aa4&0x20 前提＋入力(DAT_0228078c&0x700 持続 or DAT_02281e72>>6)で1返す",
    "0x6f42c0": "net_session_task_sm_on_touch = title touch 時に spawn する network/MMGP session SM(param_1[5]=接続obj を vtable 駆動, state0-5)。credit scene は生成せず attract 循環のみ(scene_diag 実証 2026-06-30)",
